ent improvement compared to no\nassimilation, but varied relative to the previous day autoregressive forecast\nduring the dry year 2014.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 Dec 2019 05:50:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-10"}
