al proof that only utilizes\nbasic connectedness estimates involving the James filtration and the\nBlakers-Massey Theorem, while the second reduces to the classical computational\nproof.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 Dec 2019 15:39:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 1 Apr 2020 18:24:36 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 21 Apr 2020 15:21:34 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 18 Nov 2020 04:47:17 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Wed, 15 Dec 2021 00:57:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-16"}
