cision spurious-free, demodulated\nwavefront. We show that our artifact-free, temporal-spatial quadrature\nfiltering, accomplishes an equivalent wavefront precision as the one obtained\nfrom floating-point linear phase-shifting interferometry.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 8 Dec 2019 21:48:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-11"}
